    "headline": "Illumia Wins 2025 Ellucian Partner Award for Integration Excellence",
    "summary": "SCOTTSDALE, Ariz., April 20, 2026--Illumia, formerly known as Transact + CBORD, an award-winning leader in innovative higher education, healthcare, senior living, and corporate technology, today announced it has received the 2025 Ellucian Partner Award for Integration Excellence. The award recognizes Illumia’s fully bidirectional, real-time integration between Illumia Integrated Payments and Ellucian Student, powered by Colleague, that helps keep student financial data continuously synchronized",
